translation.Name: Fishing Rod Mk.III
translation.Description: Used to catch <color=#64c819>Quest Fish</color> and <color=#64c819>Crafting Items</color> in the <color=#64c819>Fisherman's Grove</color> or <color=#64c819>Floating Island</color>. Better than the <color=#4b64fa>Fishing Rod Mk.I</color> and <color=#c832fa>Fishing Rod Mk.II</color>.
